EWC + ER combined baseline (--method ewc_er / EWCER).  seed 42, lr=1e-3, ep=5, buffer=1000, 1 seed.
Results recorded from the runs during the session (er baselines reproduce prior work bit-for-bit:
task-IL er and class-IL er match results/pt5_iter3.log at the same settings). Regenerate with:
  uv run python results/ewc_er_baseline.py > results/ewc_er_baseline.log
lambda: Adam λ=1e5 (CLConfig default); SGD λ=1e3 (default 1e5 collapses under SGD).

